solution:
八边形可以分成五个正方形和四个半正方形，每个形状的边长为 $\sqrt{2}/2$，因此其面积为 \[
\left(5 + 4 \cdot \frac{1}{2}\right) \left(\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\right)^2 = \boxed{\frac{7}{2}}.
\]

[asy]
unitsize(2cm);
for (int i=0; i<4; ++i) {
for (int j=0; j<4; ++j) {
draw((i,0)--(i,3),dashed);
draw((0,j)--(3,j),dashed);
};}
draw((1,0)--(2,0)--(3,1)--(3,2)--(2,3)--(1,3)--(0,2)--(0,1)--cycle,linewidth(0.7));
for (int i=0; i<2; ++i) {
label("1",(0.5+2i,2.5),S);
label("1",(0.5+2i,0.5),N);}
label("$\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}$",(0,1.5),E);
label("$\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}$",(3,1.5),W);
[/asy]
